entries.femaleVariant: Nah, don't like this. How come she's not here yet? She said everything went fine...
Chill. If somethin' went wrong, they woulda come for us already.
Besides, she's one of the best. You know she zeroed that asshole from the board?
Don't give a shit who she zeroed. If Brown gets word of this job, it's...
It's his word against ours. They can't prove a thing.
Even if they did, she wouldn't talk. Mercs who talk don't get gigs.
